Dear TIM Students,
Good evening!
Thank you so much for your interest in the Application Portfolio Management=
 (APM) opportunity, and a special thanks to those who attended the seminar =
yesterday!
For your reference, I=92ve attached the slide deck from the seminar.
This weekend, I=92ll be sending out details on opportunities to develop TIM=
 projects in the APM domain. These will be especially relevant for students=
 registered in TIMG 5110 this Fall.
Warm regards,
Tony B.

